China's Top Legislator Meets Tonga Guests 
Li Peng, chairman of the National People's Congress (NPC) Standing
Committee, met with a delegation led by Veikune, speaker of the Tonga
Legislative Assembly, here this afternoon.
The meeting is still going on at press time.
Veikune and his party are here for a seven-day goodwill visit to China
at the invitation of Li.
